{"tid":1314393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳伯已絕食250小時！！！！星期一出黎幫手呀！！","createTime":"2019-07-14T06:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T09:35:01.000Z","uid":25168,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c4833efd35f61174464b31f560fe69b86a75807f","tid":1314393,"uid":25168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:53:06.000Z","msg":"在金鐘海富中心留守多時、已絕食 250 小時的陳伯今日受訪時指，自己身體狀況仍然良好，各位不用擔心。陳伯向記者表示，他周一黃昏將會苦行至禮賓府， 如林鄭這樣也不肯接見他們，人人都會目睹政府如何賤視民意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6OgggyS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6OgggyS.png&h=707d6fc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f51daca640e21d24b5faf482731c5d60b11512b","tid":1314393,"uid":25168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:54:06.000Z","msg":"【反送中絕食分享】現新增了一個Telegram頻道，以分享絕食過程中的點滴，同時作為資訊傳遞的渠道，方便同路人前來支援或探望: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hungerstrike_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhungerstrike_hk&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXParktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=ff508d15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hungerstrike_hk</a>"},{"pid":"9c580bdead7b71fe72a6160e4c9a124061555b54","tid":1314393,"uid":56490,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:55:12.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"1c6ab2afe1cdb931ecd56306c7fc8b022aa6a71b","tid":1314393,"uid":25168,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:58:11.000Z","msg":"雖然成日有人會話絕食無用<br />\n但對伯伯同視障人士黎講<br />\n絕食已經非常非常勇武啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋對我地其實都有好大既幫助<br />\n就係我哋文宣時候多樣好重要既point<br />\n可以話我哋咩都試過哂<br />\n和平靜坐，絕食，苦行都試過<br />\n但政府都唔聽<br />\n所以先武力升級，衝擊等等<br />\n<br />\n雖然明知林鄭唔會理<br />\n林鄭正仆街<br />\n但我地都要支持陳伯呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9fcb672b43af6d340e84e3a1b68756c0c7552a","tid":1314393,"uid":25168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e7zBgA5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe7zBgA5.png&h=2df12a1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33208e29773571808510e72684a703ebef1fe685","tid":1314393,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071a08b88a9fef901351dca1ab54eefa487e0568","tid":1314393,"uid":69719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e09d9e566859d9b7ae9e0a9f08907917d867dc4","tid":1314393,"uid":25168,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"33208e29773571808510e72684a703ebef1fe685","tid":1314393,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:03:13.000Z","msg":"甘地都曾經絕食21日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但一定對身體非常唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5dc44547fb6287693e8d82dce83f6934294582","tid":1314393,"uid":92697,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n聽日抽時間過嚟支持"},{"pid":"22be7234db34dcad64d17bb254826f32c58f4121","tid":1314393,"uid":25168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:34:18.000Z","msg":"邊個on9逐個回覆負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hk